;
Fund DetailBank of Baroda’s on the go wearable payment solution, bob World Wave is designed to ensure expedient and seamless digital payments with just a tap on the device to meet the demands of our evolving customers. Customers can make payments on-the-go of up to INR 5,000/- without any PIN while shopping on any PoS machines enabled for contactless payments making it extremely convenient for the customers....', 'file_chunk_index': 0}

{'Fund': 'bob World Wave - A Wearable Contactless Payment Smart Watch : Fees & Charges
